title.label: EA is just not a good company anymore

content.label: This game has constant bugs/glitches.  The gameplay this season is pathetically bad, and it‚Äôs so confusing how it continually gets worse from year to year.  The matches are overly scripted, to the point of being pointless to play.  The events are boring and repetitive, although it doesn‚Äôt matter much since they never get released on-time and most of them are only helpful to paying players anyway.  The reward system makes no sense, since the items take too long to acquire and are well outdated by the time you get them.  EA either steals from player accounts, or items magically disappear.  EA has been going downhill steadily for years, but this season is simply unplayable.  Unless you want to spent a ton of real money on EA‚Äôs gambling system, deemed illegal in several countries, don‚Äôt waste your time.  EA is just not a good, or even reputable, company under their current leadership.  Please give up your licensing agreements so that a competent and ethical can have the ability to release the games players want; you are clearly not able to anymore.  This game has become complete garbage.
